body:
I dont know if this thread is going to go anywhere, but here's how it works.

1. Confess to the person above you something you've always wanted to tell them. 

2. Only positive/appropriate confessions.

3. You can have a little fun with it, or it can be a legit confession. Whatever floats your boat.

4. If a confession is personal, you MUST be respectful. Don't go "Wow you like him/her? Thats creepy EEWWW" or something in the sort. Be nice. If it does end up getting out of hand, I'll archive it.

5. Cheers!
